OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny daytime
OL,6,Fshowers soon fading this evening to
OL,7,Fleave a dry night with some lengthy
OL,8,Fclear spells. Turning chilly with
OL,9,Flight winds and a patchy frost in
OL,10,Fprone rural spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA bright, chilly start.
OL,13,FLater in the afternoon, cloud will
OL,14,Fincrease from the west later to bring
OL,15,Fsome outbreaks of rain across all
OL,16,Fparts from late evening, clearing
OL,17,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
