OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday,
OL,6,Fdry and bright start, some heavy
OL,7,Fshowers arriving later in the day.
OL,8,FMonday, variable cloud and showers.
OL,9,FRain and strong winds overnight, then
OL,10,Fbreezy with showers Tuesday.
